data.description: Lovely manufactured home with great views of West Tucson and enjoy the serenity of the nature surrounding it. Short drive over to the Casino Del Sol, and close to Ajo Way to ride straight into the city. Backyard is long and narrow, and a shed that can be connected to the electric of the house and a smaller metal storage shed. The house is like a pie-shape. There is a gas grill in the back for a good cookout.
